<font color="#ff80ff">느껴져요</font>

443
01:43:02,168 --> 01:43:03,668
<font color="#ff80ff">보여요?</font>
<font color="#0000ff">보여요!</font>

444
01:43:04,144 --> 01:43:05,351
<font color="#0000ff">확실히 들어가고 있어요</font>

445
01:43:06,299 --> 01:43:07,608
<font color="#ff80ff">어디에 넣고 있죠?</font>

446
