<font color="#ff80ff">기분 좋아</font>

454
01:44:40,652 --> 01:44:41,859
<font color="#0000ff">좋아요</font>

455
01:45:18,437 --> 01:45:19,405
<font color="#0000ff">위에서 더 해줘요</font>

456
